2026-03-04 16:07:29:0458 [GENERATION] {{"run_id": "1772640430298-8f1592b9", "task": "dois_soma", "attempt": 1, "tokens_input": 157, "tokens_output": 54, "tokens_total": 211}} <code>
    def two_sum(nums, target):
        seen = {}
        for i, num in enumerate(nums):
            complement = target - num
            if complement in seen:
                return [seen[complement], i]
            seen[num] = i
        return []
    </code>

